shellkeep (0.3.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Rewrite in Rust with iced UI and russh SSH
  * Decompose app state into focused sub-structs
  * Complete ConnectionState/TabBackend enum migration
  * Add 127 unit tests
  * Add structured error context to SSH errors

